{"tid":860683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五旬大叔大嬸網戀閃婚成佳話 網民︰根本是父女戀","createTime":"2018-10-13T13:58:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T15:12:49.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"205700c8575a6657c21b4cda2e59b140ae5f6dab","tid":860683,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T13:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/13/215806_3a47eee48ce98ef7bd52abb1c4644519.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F13%2F215806_3a47eee48ce98ef7bd52abb1c4644519.png&h=42aa5bfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n家住雲南曲靖市的51歲教師譚永莉，上月在網上認識同齡網友田曉奇後，因對方的甜蜜告白，便決心下嫁，結果她們認識第7日就登記結婚。這種網戀閃婚故事在網上引起爭議，惟不少網民聚焦譚永莉的「童顏」之上，有網民更直言︰「根本就是一對父女戀」。<br />\n<br />\n田曉奇接受內地傳媒採訪時表示，他是一名網上主播，在某網上影片平台上結識了譚永莉，便被對方的聲音迷倒，連日來不斷找譚永莉傾電話。至於譚永莉則指，讓她下定泱心的，就是田曉奇的告白，「我真的很喜歡你很愛你，如果你跟我在一起，我會讓你一輩子快樂，我會一輩子關心你，跟你一起過到老。」<br />\n<br />\n結果，兩人認識後第3天，田曉奇就帶譚永莉見自己家人，第7天兩人就登記結婚登記結婚。譚永莉坦言，她還有4年便可以退休，待她退休後，就嫁雞隨雞，「他去哪我就去哪」。"},{"pid":"33fc904240aecea857af2f31a17f6568af9581d0","tid":860683,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9fb073e48d8a33ed77f72bcecade01e8341a7a7f","tid":860683,"uid":139126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:03:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"762b19b3cb1fe2d2a00b58e346284e1fd2a5694d","tid":860683,"uid":156911,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:11:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c3a7f90866e739641755806ecbe9bca73043be6","tid":860683,"uid":76314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33fc904240aecea857af2f31a17f6568af9581d0","tid":860683,"uid":198622,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T14:14:31.000Z","msg":"Over咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係襟老，似三十頭左右啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b80a322312a4589b124f237831c703a0ae9bfc","tid":860683,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:12:49.000Z","msg":"整撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}